# John Smith: Software Engineer

John Smith is a software engineer currently working at Google. He received a Bachelor of Science in Computer Science from Cornell University in 2010 and a Master of Engineering in Computer Science from Cornell in 2011. His experience includes software engineering at Google since 2013 where he has achieved several accomplishments, and computer repair work at Buy More from 2008 to 2012. He has strong skills in programming languages like Java, C++, and Python. His interests include data analysis, web design, and activities like piano, chess, cooking, and running.
